text: thumb Ait Ouabane is a village in the Tizi Ouzou Province in Kabylie, Algeria. ==Location== The village is surrounded by a forest in the Djurdjura mountain range.A. Talbi, La place du secteur des forêts dans le développement local, Conservation des forêts, 2008, p. 4 ==References== Category:Villages in Algeria Category:Kabylie
title: Ait Ouabane
